OL,3,CWinter fuel payment should be restored
OL,4,Cfor NI pensioners - Lyons
OL,6,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons has
OL,7,Fsaid he will be recommending that
OL,8,Fpensioners in Northern Ireland have
OL,9,Ftheir winter fuel payment restored
OL,10,Ffollowing a U-turn by the UK
OL,11,FGovernment.
OL,13,FMr Lyons said the details of
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves' decision
OL,15,Fwere still to be worked out, but added
OL,16,Fthat the "most simple and
OL,17,Fstraightforward" approach seemed to be
OL,18,Fto replicate the same approach in
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland.
