OL,3,CWinter fuel payment should be restored
OL,4,Cfor NI pensioners - Lyons
OL,6,FAround 250,000 pensioners in the
OL,7,Fregion were affected when the payment
OL,8,Fwas cut last year in a cost-saving
OL,9,Fmeasure by the new Labour government.
OL,11,FOn Monday, the Chancellor announced
OL,12,Fshe had changed course and some nine
OL,13,Fmillion pensioners in England and
OL,14,FWales will receive the winter fuel
OL,15,Fpayment this winter.
