OL,3,CWinter fuel payment should be restored
OL,4,Cfor NI pensioners - Lyons
OL,6,FThe payment, worth up to #300, will be
OL,7,Frestored to the vast majority of
OL,8,Fpensioners who previously received it
OL,9,Fbecause anyone with an income of under
OL,10,F#35,000 a year will now get the
OL,11,Fpayment automatically.
OL,13,FMr Lyons told the Northern Ireland
OL,14,FAssembly that "more clarity is needed"
OL,15,Fon how pensioners affected by previous
OL,16,Fwinter fuel payment cuts will have the
OL,17,Fbenefit reinstated.
