OL,6,FSpeaking to the media, Mr Lyons said
OL,7,Fit was "good news" that the Government
OL,8,Fhad listened to concerns over its
OL,9,Fpolicy.
OL,11,FHe said: "It is right that they have
OL,12,Fhad a think again on this. There were
OL,13,Fmany people right on the borderline of
OL,14,Fpension credit who were in need and
OL,15,Fweren't getting the support that they
OL,16,Fshould have got.
