OL,6,F"I am glad the Government has made a U-
OL,7,Fturn in relation to this."What we now
OL,8,Fneed to do is to work out what is
OL,9,Fcoming next and how that impacts upon
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,F"I met with one of the Department for
OL,13,FWork and Pensions ministers this
OL,14,Fafternoon, along with the Finance
OL,15,FMinister (John O'Dowd) and officials
OL,16,Fwill continue to work throughout the
OL,17,Fcourse of today to nail down some of
OL,18,Fthose details."
