OL,6,FPressed on whether pensioners in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland would definitely have
OL,8,Ftheir payment restored, Mr Lyons said:
OL,9,F"That will ultimately be a decision
OL,10,Ffor the Executive, but right now that
OL,11,Fis certainly what I would be
OL,12,Frecommending.
OL,14,F"That the money that will be there,
OL,15,Fthat will be available, that we allow
OL,16,Fwhat is happening in England and Wales
OL,17,Fto happen in Northern Ireland as well.
