OL,6,F"I think that is going to be the most
OL,7,Fsimple and straightforward way to do
OL,8,Fit and that is what I want to see
OL,9,Fhappen."
OL,11,FAfter the Government withdrew the
OL,12,Fpayment from many pensioners last
OL,13,Fyear, Mr Lyons announced a one-off
OL,14,F#100 fuel support payment for
OL,15,Fpensioner households in Northern
OL,16,FIreland who were no longer eligible.
