OL,6,FHe said: "It has been handled very
OL,7,Fpoorly by the Government, I don't
OL,8,Fthink anybody expected a Labour
OL,9,Fgovernment to attack pensioners in
OL,10,Fthis way.
OL,12,F"My focus was always on those who were
OL,13,Fin need, those who just about missed
OL,14,Fout because of where the boundary was
OL,15,Ffor pension credit.
OL,17,F"I met a lot of people who were
OL,18,Fworried and they were concerned and
OL,19,Fthat is why I was pleased to be able
OL,20,Fto give a little bit to help those who
OL,21,Fotherwise would have missed out.
